channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/shane-brown-97094682/xiejra-ekstrak-bipolar
(Track for @HELIXX’s EP, Helixx & Friends Vol. 1) This felt like it took forever for me and @Xiejra, but I just realized that it took only a week. Huh. This song went to so many genres. First electronic, IDM, Dubstep, so many. Me and Xiejra will appreciate feedback onto this song. You can Remix this track in Auxy!: https://app.auxy.co/projects/f4gxEgeyGqROLodqcnJllA==
